      "content": "thanks. the ibuprofen feels like it might not be enough though, the pain is really intense and it hurts even more if i try to walk or move around. i really need to get some sleep because i have work in the morning. if i take the codeine with the ibuprofen, would that help more? i don't want to go to a doctor in the middle of the night if it's just something minor like a stomach bug or bad cramps.",
